data.text:
CREATE TABLE `sa_relation_check_coupon` (
  `id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `check_site_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `store_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `coupon_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `coupon_title` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `coupon_slug` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `coupon_affiliate_url` varchar(2083) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `check_site_id` (`check_site_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=26 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `sa_relation_check_site` (
  `id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `site_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `store_count` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `coupon_count` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `site_url` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `site_id` (`site_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=187 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
